      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="572c5-102"><xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationStartingEventArgs.Pivot%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性是<xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationPivot>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="572c5-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationStartingEventArgs.Pivot%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is a <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationPivot>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="572c5-103">当您将设置<xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationStartingEventArgs.Pivot%2A>中的事件处理程序<xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationStarting>事件中，当用户在操作过程中使用一个手指，操作将包含轮换数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="572c5-103">When you set <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationStartingEventArgs.Pivot%2A> in an event handler for the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationStarting> event, the manipulation will contain rotation data when the user uses one finger during a manipulation.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="572c5-104">这是为了模拟真实情况下，可以使用一个手指来旋转对象，例如一张纸上一个表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="572c5-104">This is to simulate real-world situations where you can use one finger to rotate an object, such as a piece of paper on a table.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="572c5-105">如果<xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationStartingEventArgs.Pivot%2A>是`null`，用户必须使用两根手指进行旋转。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="572c5-105">If the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationStartingEventArgs.Pivot%2A> is `null`, the user must use two fingers to cause rotation.</span></span>  
  
   
  
